June 2011
- adjusted DB default ID values for
       500 - attrnames
       500 - attrcategories
       500 - attrcategoryvalues
       1000 -  attrvalues
       1000 -  attroptionvalues
       100  -  cabletypes
       100  -  cablecategories

This means in future we have a set range for defaults in new releases.


